column1: Baby Barnaby's////It's a Barnaby's I don't hate
column2: so that's a plus. I think they should make all the Barnaby's this kind
column3: because this is some good breakfast. The coffee comes smelling divine
column4: and the eggs are that kind of cloudy consistency that just screams for some salsa
column6: assuming you ask. Sausage comes in a couple of animal choices
column7: chicken being the surprising star here. French toast is not bad
column8: as is the breakfast tacos. Their corn beef hash
column10: must be what disappointment tastes like.
